Package com.jack.dicewars.dice_wars.ai

This package contains the framework and implementation for calling AI work in DiceWars.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    DiceWarsAi
    A DiceWarsAi can decide if it wants to continue selecting Selectables, and then request that they be selected.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractAi
    This superclass of DiceWars AI takes a Game to analyze and request selections from.
    SimpleAi
    This SimpleAi will take select the first Selectable it can get to and only attack if it has a higher attack value than it's opponent.
